headline: ONCOR TO RELEASE SECOND QUARTER 2025 RESULTS AUGUST 7
summary: Oncor Electric Delivery Company LLC ("Oncor") plans to release its second quarter 2025 results on August 7, prior to Sempra's (NYSE: SRE) second quarter 2025 results conference call. Oncor's earnings release will be available on Oncor's website, oncor.com.
